com.tibco.tea.agent.server

Class TeaAgentServlet

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.servlet.GenericServlet
      • javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
        • com.tibco.tea.agent.server.TeaAgentServlet
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler, javax.servlet.Servlet, javax.servlet.ServletConfig

    public abstract class TeaAgentServlet
extends javax.servlet.http.HttpServlet
implements Thread.UncaughtExceptionHandler

    TeaAgent that can be registered in a Servlet container.

    Servlets expects the following init parameters:

    name
    Name of the agent type as string
    version
    Version of the agent type as string
    agent-info
    String providing information about the agent
    enable-metrics
    Boolean indicating if the agent VM metrics should be enabled
    static-resources-location
    location on disk of the static resources server by this agent

    To control the instances that are registered to the agent must override the method getObjectInstances() to return an array of instances that need to be registered.

    See Also:
